    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are accepted as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for Class II devices at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support regulatory submission identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. RH index predictions are within 15% of experimental benchmarks, GCI is below 2%, and worst-case identification is robust to input variation. The credibility assessment team unanimously accepts the model for the stated COU.",
